<tr>
  <td class='header'>
    Congrats with your new <%= project_type_name(@project) %>
  </td>
</tr>
<tr>
  <td class='text left'>
    <table class='md-table' align='center'>
      <tr>
        <td>
          You have approved the files, which means your project <%= cut_on_word(@project.name) %> has come to an end. Please don’t be a stranger, we would love to hear from you, and hope you have more projects in mind for us. You can download your files below & don’t forget to keep them in a safe place!
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </td>
</tr>
<tr>
  <td class='padding-bottom-25'>
    <a href='<%= "#{host_url}/c/projects/#{@project.id}/files" %>' class='main-btn'>
      Open Project

      <%= image_tag 'arrow_white.png', class: 'arrow' %>
    </a>
  </td>
</tr>
